Jhin is flourishing right now, because he is an adc-ASSASSIN, he is **designed to kill squishies**, in a squishy meta, with a squishy-killing item buff! He's _terrible at literally every other ADC responsibility_. He dies if he even sees a tank. Balance him with care.

